---
// Four parent-coded reassurances. Order matters: lead with proof, end with safety.
const proofs = [
  {
    big: "5",
    label: "students per cohort",
    note: "A hard limit. Not a marketing number.",
  },
  {
    big: "4",
    label: "weekends only",
    note: "Saturdays and Sundays. School week untouched.",
  },
  {
    big: "2 hrs",
    label: "per live session",
    note: "Long enough to finish something every time.",
  },
  {
    big: "₹99",
    label: "to attend the first class",
    note: "A live look. You and your child decide after.",
  },
];
---

<section
  id="promise"
  aria-labelledby="promise-heading"
  class="section-pad"
  style="background: var(--color-paper);"
>
  <div class="container-page grid items-end gap-10 md:grid-cols-12 md:gap-16">
    <div class="md:col-span-7">
      <p class="eyebrow reveal">For parents</p>
      <h2
        id="promise-heading"
        class="reveal mt-4"
        style={`font-size: var(--text-3xl); --reveal-delay: 80ms; line-height: 1.04;`}
      >
        You don't have to take our word for it.<br />
        <span style="color: var(--color-ink-soft); font-weight: 500;">You'll see it.</span>
      </h2>
      <p
        class="reveal mt-6 max-w-xl"
        style={`font-size: var(--text-lg); color: var(--color-ink-soft); --reveal-delay: 140ms;`}
      >
        Two weeks in, your child will show you a working agent on their laptop. By week four, you'll be in the audience for demo day — watching the project they built, live, with a real URL anyone in the world can visit.
      </p>
    </div>

    <p
      class="reveal md:col-span-5"
      style={`color: var(--color-ink-soft); font-size: var(--text-base); border-left: 2px solid var(--color-accent); padding-left: 1rem; --reveal-delay: 200ms;`}
    >
      Most courses end with a PDF certificate and a feeling that not much happened. Logic Labs ends with something your child can show you, show their school, and put on a college application.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div
    class="container-page mt-14"
  >
    <dl
      class="reveal grid gap-px overflow-hidden rounded-[var(--radius-lg)] border"
      style="background: var(--color-rule); border-color: var(--color-rule); grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(220px, 1fr)); --reveal-delay: 260ms;"
    >
      {proofs.map((p) => (
        <div
          class="p-7"
          style="background: var(--color-paper-card);"
        >
          <dt
            class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.12em]"
            style="color: var(--color-ink-mute);"
          >
            {p.label}
          </dt>
          <dd
            class="mt-3"
            style={`font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: var(--text-3xl); font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: -0.03em; color: var(--color-ink); line-height: 1;`}
          >
            {p.big}
          </dd>
          <p
            class="mt-3"
            style={`color: var(--color-ink-soft); font-size: var(--text-sm); line-height: 1.5;`}
          >
            {p.note}
          </p>
        </div>
      ))}
    </dl>
  </div>
</section>
